ribbonwood
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Hoheria papulnea </i>
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka Lacebark.  The tallest of three main ribbonwoods / lacebarks (12 metres), natural distribution just north half of north island.
